    detail: "Our marketing agency serves B2B SaaS clients, and we were using separate tools for social listening (Mention), prospecting (Apollo), outreach (Instantly), and CRM (HubSpot). Typpout replaced the first three entirely. The AI-generated outreach messages reference the prospect's exact social post, which makes the reply rate insanely high. Our clients are thrilled with the pipeline quality.",
    name: "Swapnil",
    handle: "@swapnil_mktg",
    role: "CEO",
    company: "DigiMatrix Marketing",
    init: "SW",
    bg: "bg-pink-100",
    txt: "text-pink-700",
    border: "border-pink-200",
    metric: "4 tools replaced",
    metricLabel: "Consolidated into Typpout",
  },
  {
    text: "Speed matters. Typpout helped us move from idea to pipeline in days. The AI outreach felt personal — we closed our first 3 customers directly from campaigns.",
    detail: "We were launching a new product line and needed pipeline fast. Traditional outbound would have taken weeks to set up: buy a list, write sequences, warm up domains. With Typpout, we configured our ICP on Monday, the social listener started finding signals on Tuesday, and we had our first demo booked by Wednesday. The speed-to-pipeline is unlike anything I've experienced in 10 years of B2B sales.",
    name: "Sanskar Pitta",
    handle: "@sanskarpitta",
    role: "Sales Lead",
    company: "Nemetschek Group",
    init: "SK",
    bg: "bg-yellow-100",
    txt: "text-yellow-700",
    border: "border-yellow-200",
    metric: "3 days to pipeline",
    metricLabel: "From setup to first demo",
  },
  {
    text: "We were spending 3 hours a day manually monitoring LinkedIn. Typpout cut that to zero and the quality of leads went up. The ICP matching is genuinely impressive.",
    detail: "My team of 4 SDRs was manually scrolling LinkedIn, X, and industry forums looking for buying signals. Each rep spent about 3 hours per day on this. Typpout automated the entire process and actually finds signals we were missing — competitor mentions in X threads, hiring signals on LinkedIn, and even funding announcements on Crunchbase. The AI catches patterns a human would overlook.",
    name: "Priya Mehta",
    handle: "@priyamehta_rev",
    role: "Head of Revenue",
    company: "ScaleUp Partners",
    init: "PM",
    bg: "bg-purple-100",
    txt: "text-purple-700",
    border: "border-purple-200",
    metric: "12 hrs/day saved",
    metricLabel: "Across the SDR team",
  },
  {
    text: "Our reply rate jumped from 12% to 47% within the first month. The AI replies are fast and on-brand — prospects can't even tell it's automated until they're already on the calendar.",
