    name: "James Okafor",
    handle: "@jamesokafor",
    role: "VP Sales",
    company: "Growthbase",
    init: "JO",
    bg: "bg-orange-100",
    txt: "text-orange-700",
    border: "border-orange-200",
    metric: "47% reply rate",
    metricLabel: "Up from 12% with cold email",
  },
  {
    text: "I was skeptical about AI outreach tools but Typpout actually delivers. It picked up a competitor switch signal on X and booked a demo before we even knew the prospect existed.",
    detail: "A VP of Sales at a Series B company tweeted about frustrations with their current outbound tool. Typpout detected the signal, matched it to our ICP, and sent a contextual DM within 45 seconds. The prospect replied 'yes, let's talk' within 10 minutes. That deal closed at $48K ARR. We would have completely missed this prospect with our existing prospecting workflow.",
    name: "Lauren Park",
    handle: "@laurenpark_gtm",
    role: "Demand Gen Manager",
    company: "Nextera Systems",
    init: "LP",
    bg: "bg-indigo-100",
    txt: "text-indigo-700",
    border: "border-indigo-200",
    metric: "$48K deal closed",
    metricLabel: "From a single X signal",
  },
  {
    text: "Finally a GTM tool that doesn't feel like it was designed for a 100-person sales team. Perfect for our lean 3-person GTM team. We punch way above our weight now.",
    detail: "As a seed-stage startup with 3 people doing everything, we can't afford dedicated SDRs or expensive sales tools. Typpout's Solo plan at $99/mo gives us enterprise-level social selling capabilities. The AI Reply Agent handles conversations while we focus on product and customer success. We've grown from 0 to 30 customers in 4 months, all through Typpout-sourced pipeline.",
    name: "Marcus Webb",
    handle: "@marcuswebb",
    role: "Founder",
    company: "Synthos AI",
    init: "MW",
    bg: "bg-teal-100",
    txt: "text-teal-700",
    border: "border-teal-200",
    metric: "0 to 30 customers",
    metricLabel: "In 4 months with 3-person team",
  },
  {
