    metric: "5 deals from signals",
    metricLabel: "Closed from funding alerts",
  },
  {
    text: "Typpout's multi-platform monitoring is what sold us. We were missing half our signals by only watching LinkedIn. X and Instagram have been goldmines for our B2B motion.",
